text: Olivia DeJonge (; born 30 April 1998) is an Australian actress. She is known for playing Tara Swift / Shaneen Quigg in ABC1's Hiding, Becca in The Visit (2015), Elle in Netflix's The Society and Priscilla Presley in the biopic movie Elvis (2022). ==Filmography== * Good Pretender (2011) ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:1998 births Category:Australian child actors Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Actors from Melbourne
